---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Navigation from '../../components/Navigation.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Partner - Companies">
  <Navigation />
  <main>
    <section class="partner-hero">
      <div class="container">
        <h1>partner with us: companies</h1>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="companies-partner">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="partner-content">
          <h2>why partner with the tech bros</h2>
          <p class="section-intro">We work with companies who want access to technical women they wouldn't otherwise meet.</p>
          <p>Our events are not broad, open meetups. They are highly curated, technical-first spaces that attract senior engineers, researchers, and early-stage founders across AI, robotics, deep tech, and applied science.</p>
          
          <h3>partnering with us gives you:</h3>
          <ul class="partner-list">
            <li>Direct access to a hard-to-reach technical talent pool</li>
            <li>High-signal brand exposure in a trusted community</li>
            <li>A credible way to support women in tech without performative initiatives</li>
          </ul>

          <h2>what partnership looks like</h2>
          <p>You sponsor a one-off event that we design with you, aligned to your goals.</p>
          
          <h3>typical formats include:</h3>
          <ul class="partner-list">
            <li>Hackathons</li>
            <li>Technical conferences or panels</li>
            <li>Co-working and community days</li>
          </ul>
          <p>We handle curation, audience quality, and delivery. You show up to the right room.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <div class="spotlight-hero-image">
      <img 
        src="/partner/bang-olufsen-hackathon-hero.jpg" 
        alt="Bang & Olufsen Hackathon"
        fetchpriority="high"
        loading="eager"
        decoding="async"
        width="1920"
        height="1080"
      />
    </div>

    <section class="spotlight-section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="spotlight-content">
          <div class="spotlight-images-left">
            <img src="/partner/bang-olufsen-1.jpg" alt="Bang & Olufsen Hackathon" />
            <img src="/partner/bang-olufsen-2.jpg" alt="Bang & Olufsen Hackathon" />
            <img src="/partner/bang-olufsen-3.jpg" alt="Bang & Olufsen Hackathon" />
          </div>
          <div class="spotlight-text-column">
            <h2>spotlight: bang & olufsen hackathon</h2>
            <p>We partnered with Bang & Olufsen on a bespoke hackathon bringing together technical women across hardware, AI, and engineering.</p>
            <div class="spotlight-stats">
              <div class="spotlight-stat">
                <div class="spotlight-number">25</div>
                <div class="spotlight-label">participants</div>
              </div>
              <div class="spotlight-stat">
                <div class="spotlight-number">73%</div>
                <div class="spotlight-label">CS / AI / Engineering background</div>
              </div>
              <div class="spotlight-stat">
                <div class="spotlight-number">4.6 / 5</div>
                <div class="spotlight-label">Average event rating</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p>The event created meaningful technical engagement, high-quality conversations, and strong brand alignment without feeling like a recruitment fair.</p>
            
            <div class="spotlight-quotes">
              <blockquote>"It was ABSOLUTELY FANTASTIC to have an all woman event! Had some great meaningful conversations that wouldn't regularly pop up in mixed events! Great to get other girls inputs and experiences of the STEM industry ðŸ§¡This was a true pleasure!"</blockquote>
              <blockquote>"Keep it going, you make such a great impact ðŸ’—"</blockquote>
              <blockquote>"Thank you for hosting this and we expect more hackathons in the future :)"</blockquote>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="companies-partner">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="partner-content">

          <div class="text-center" style="margin-top: 3rem;">
            <a href="mailto:team@thetechbros.io" class="btn">Get in Touch</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .partner-hero {
    padding: 6rem 0 3rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .hero-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-top: 1rem;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  .companies-partner {
    padding: 4rem 0;
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
  }

  .partner-content {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .partner-content h2 {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-top: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    font-size: 1.8rem;
  }

  .partner-content h2:first-of-type {
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  .partner-content h3 {
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-top: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
  }

  .section-intro {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--color-text);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .partner-content p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  .partner-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding-left: 0;
    margin: 1.5rem 0;
  }

  .partner-list li {
    padding: 0.75rem 0;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.7;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
  }

  .partner-list li::before {
    content: 'â†’';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .spotlight-hero-image {
    width: 100%;
    margin: 4rem 0;
  }

  .spotlight-hero-image img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .spotlight-section {
    padding: 4rem 0;
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
  }

  .spotlight-content {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.5fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .spotlight-images-left {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .spotlight-images-left img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
    border-radius: 8px;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .spotlight-text-column h2 {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-top: 0;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .spotlight-quotes {
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .spotlight-quotes blockquote {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    border-left: 3px solid var(--color-primary);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
  }

  .spotlight-stats {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 2rem;
    margin: 2rem 0;
  }

  .spotlight-stat {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .spotlight-number {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(239, 31, 159, 0.5);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .spotlight-label {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .spotlight-stats {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .spotlight-content {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .spotlight-text-column {
      order: 1;
    }

    .spotlight-images-left {
      order: 2;
    }
  }
</style>
